values: Sorry guys, I no longer have the time to keep up with this journal. You can read my public journal here. I update at least three times a week, no matter how busy I am.

Sorry guys, this journal is FRIENDS ONLY. I'm picky about the maturity level of my readers. Here is where I store my more personal thoughts about life. Some of them will be turned into actual songs, others will just rest here. I also have a bit of profanity here and there, so I won't grant access to the 13 year olds, etc. If you want to gain access to my entries, just leave a comment telling me who you are and add me to your friends list. I'll most likely add you back. Live, love and rock the f*ck out! - Raivyn
